Phase 2 verdict:
  Default-cell T_pred (15.9) is 4.0× the FCS measured period 4.
  Single-pole H(ω) systematically over-estimates the ringing
  period — likely because the FCS 5-tap windowed integrator
  introduces faster effective dynamics than a single-pole
  low-pass with τ_m=2.35 captures. Best tolerance 8.00
  gives Jaccard 0.238, vs strict-tol Jaccard 0.000.
